{"tid":2407384,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅致光料失業率達七，惟不考慮失業援助金","createTime":"2021-02-14T04:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T04:10:25.000Z","uid":278587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a10030f5071c976b5a9ebf07e334efe6eb47bc97","tid":2407384,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T04:10:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=424001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424001&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=31c91955\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424001&h=91367f89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=424001</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】勞工及福利局局長羅致光預料失業率或會高於百分之七，但指勞工界爭取的失業援助金並非公平的機制，政府不會採納。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光：「以失業率作為界線很古怪的。作為臨時的制度，如果(失業率)跌到4.99%就不能取，不關你事，因為整體到4.99%你就不能取，這是很古怪的。用時限又很古怪，12月31日可以領取，1月1日就不能取。對不起，你遲了一日失業，你就取不到，你說為何老闆不早些解僱你呢。」"}]}